name: Courteney Cox (Late 80s/Early 90s)
description:
Courteney Cox is an American actress known for the sitcom Friends and the film franchise Scream, amongst many other roles.

My goal with this TI was to capture her looks in the late 80s and early 90s.

I trained the TI for 1000 steps, but it got overtrained pretty soon and I ended up setting for step 400, which might still be very slightly overtrained too, but looks really accurate in my opinion. In any case, I recommend using the embedding at a reduced weight. For instance, type "(c0urt400:0.99)" in your prompt. That should solve any issue in most cases.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
